Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.50,0:01:35.49,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(890,600)\be4}第23话 「随风而逝的战士」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}风…怎么…被吸进瓦姆乌的管子里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终流法——浑楔飒！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是风吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你在火坛边上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo 我只能把握到你大概的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.28,0:02:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现在你停止了波纹的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我横扫过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一定能找到你的身体 切成两半
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑楔飒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.92,0:02:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦姆乌的最终流法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不同于让身体透明的用法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这招是吸入大量的风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在肺内部极度压缩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再从窄如剃刀的缝隙中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以超高压强喷射出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说 是一道烈风之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 风的高速压缩带来的摩擦和热力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是瓦姆乌的肉体也无法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会慢慢地受破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那凄惨的样子 实在太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢下这场战斗 用人类的生命治愈自己的伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想办法反抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.91,0:02:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我称为 波纹油作战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的体内 可以说是一个超浓缩的氧气瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把这火焰瓶扔向他的管子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就会把火吸进去 引起体内爆炸！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这也是我的最终策略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.73,0:03:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦失败就要完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NWWW 找到了 在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 吃招！瓦姆乌！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰瓶吗 没意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要离开火坛有一米距离
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能感受到物体的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经束手无策了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你刚才的喊声 让我确定到你的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.86,0:03:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！浑楔飒！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西——撒——！靠你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要丢火种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你丢什么 在我1米范围内就能察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我现在就把你切断 就分出胜负！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JoJo！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终…终于赢了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:14.58,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Ovunque tu vada
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:20.86,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Ovunque io vada
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:26.87,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}C'é il mio amor nella tua vita,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:34.30,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}c'é I'amor nella tua giornata
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:42.94,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Basta un tuo sorriso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:49.54,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}un tuo sol sorriso
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:58.08,insert,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Non morirà I'alma mia. é immortal!
