Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:18.30,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.30,0:22:25.56,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:36.14,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}The music dance and sing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:39.98,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}They make the children really ring
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.03,0:22:45.43,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}I spend the day your way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.43,0:22:52.00,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Call it morning driving thru the sound and in and out the valley
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.66,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}In and around the lake
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.71,0:22:59.82,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Mountains come out of the sky and they stand there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.79,0:23:06.58,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}One mile over we'll be there and we'll see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:13.01,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Ten true summers we'll be there and laughing too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.70,0:23:22.25,EDE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)\be1}Twenty four before my love you'll see I'll be there with you
