Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(300,300)}我只想轻轻松松地杀死你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(300,300)}这把火就是一个赌注！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.54,0:23:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,690)\fad(300,300)}这孩子…唯有这个孩子…
